OL,4,Chospital aims to cut #67m
OL,6,FOvertime pay and free tea and coffee
OL,7,Fhave been slashed at Derriford
OL,8,FHospital, as it aims to save nearly
OL,9,F#70million this year.
OL,11,FBosses at University Hospitals
OL,12,FPlymouth NHS Trust have told staff
OL,13,Fthey need to reduce costs by
OL,14,F#67million as part of wider NHS
OL,15,Fcutbacks.
OL,17,FThe trust, which employs 11,000
OL,18,Fpeople, said #34million will be cut
OL,19,Ffrom pay - including overtime and
OL,20,Fstaff incentives.
