OL,6,FDespite fears about job losses and
OL,7,Fhaving an impact on patient care,
OL,8,Finterim chief executive Mark Hackett
OL,9,Ftold ITV News West Country the cuts
OL,10,Fwere necessary.
OL,12,F'We are facing a tough year' - chief
OL,13,Fexecutive
OL,15,F"We have always had an historic
OL,16,Fdeficit that we need to address, but
OL,17,Fwe are facing a really tough year in
OL,18,Fterms of public expenditure," he said.
