OL,6,F"That's affecting the hospital, and
OL,7,Fwe're going to need to look much more
OL,8,Fat the use of our resources.
OL,10,F"We face a really tough challenge this
OL,11,Fyear in trying to find #67million.
OL,12,FLast year, we saved #56million but
OL,13,Fwhat people need to recognise is we
OL,14,Fare a large organisation that runs on
OL,15,F#1.2billion per year.
OL,17,F"There are many improvements we need
OL,18,Fto make. The hospital has made huge
OL,19,Fstrides in improving its services last
OL,20,Fyear, despite saving #56million.
