OL,6,F"I do think we can make the
OL,7,Fimprovements and changes to improve
OL,8,Fpatient access while also looking at
OL,9,Four resources differently."
OL,11,FFollowing this story, it is clear this
OL,12,Fis a difficult time for everyone at
OL,13,FDerriford Hospital.
OL,15,FLast week, I reported on the trust's
OL,16,Fannouncement that nearly #70million
OL,17,Fneeded to be saved, by reducing the
OL,18,Fpay bill and 'increasing productivity'.
