OL,6,FBut now further information has come
OL,7,Fto light after we obtained an email
OL,8,Fsent to all staff by the interim chief
OL,9,Fexecutive Mark Hackett.
OL,11,FThis email included details about the
OL,12,F'immediate' spending cuts and Mr
OL,13,FHackett acknowledged the "anxiety and
OL,14,Fanguish" felt by staff.
OL,16,FOne staff member, who wishes to remain
OL,17,Fanonymous, told us: "It's an absolute
OL,18,Fmassacre of what the NHS is and an
OL,19,Finsult to what it stands for".
