OL,6,FWhen interviewing Mr Hackett, I asked
OL,7,Fif these cuts would lead to
OL,8,Fredundancies to which he replied that
OL,9,Fit was "too early to say" and was
OL,10,Fadamant there would be no impact on
OL,11,Fpatient care.
OL,13,FStaff are hoping this really is the
OL,14,Fcase, as these "significant' spendings
OL,15,Fcuts come into force.
OL,17,FWhat is being cut?
OL,19,FIn a bid to cut costs, hospital bosses
OL,20,Fwill:
