OL,6,FAccording to an email sent to staff,
OL,7,Fseen by ITV News West Country,
OL,8,Fstopping free tea, coffee and juice
OL,9,Fdrinks will save the hospital around
OL,10,F#100,000 per year.
OL,12,FAsked about concerns the cuts will
OL,13,Fnegatively impact patient care, Mr
OL,14,FHackett said: "I would completely
OL,15,Frefute that - that's not true.
OL,17,F"We're actually increasing the
OL,18,Fstandards of services to our patients
OL,19,Fdespite having to make these economies.
