OL,6,F"We're not reducing the standards of
OL,7,Fcare, we're improving them and what I
OL,8,Fwould recognise is that staff are
OL,9,Fanxious at this time.
OL,11,F"That's completely understandable and
OL,12,Fwe will do the very best we can to
OL,13,Fcommunicate with them as quickly and
OL,14,Fswiftly as we can what the impact of
OL,15,Fthe changes are on them."
OL,17,FHowever, Mr Hackett was unable to say
OL,18,Fif redundancies will be necessary.
